  "detailed_description": "<strong>Break Games</strong> is designed so every Twitch creator can take a break. Start a game, and let your viewers play it. Rotate between 3 different games to keep it fresh. Doesn't matter if you have 1 viewer or 100.000. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/1d299140e4aac56c003362a096797ae4.poster.avif?t=1750364928\" width=624 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/1d299140e4aac56c003362a096797ae4.webm?t=1750364928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/1d299140e4aac56c003362a096797ae4.mp4?t=1750364928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> Cuby is a cute bouncing cube that will swipe away emotes placed by viewers. Emotes that survive Cuby's bouncing rage will gain points! You can also use your profile picture or let it switch between your emotes.<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/710da5eb865926026b90d44dc212dd6d.poster.avif?t=1750364928\" width=624 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/710da5eb865926026b90d44dc212dd6d.webm?t=1750364928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/710da5eb865926026b90d44dc212dd6d.mp4?t=1750364928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> While you are working on the toilet, your viewers are coordinating the defense against alien domination! Look at them go, working together to prioritise targets and reach a new high score.<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/b62eedd9679ff813499e8620c04017be.poster.avif?t=1750364928\" width=624 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/b62eedd9679ff813499e8620c04017be.webm?t=1750364928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/b62eedd9679ff813499e8620c04017be.mp4?t=1750364928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> Dance until you are hit! Who will dance to victory? Perfect for hosting a giveaway. Alternatively, announce 3 options, type !start to play Victory Dance, go take a break, and let the winning viewer decide your next game. <br><br>Take a break while not stressing about decreasing numbers #selfcare💜routine. <br>✅Keeps viewers engaged<br>✅Mods can start new games.<br>✅Replace your countdown timer before the stream starts. Play a game instead.<br><br><strong>DISCLAIMER: Break Games is designed for creators on Twitch, no matter the audience size.</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Break Games</strong> is designed so every Twitch creator can take a break. Start a game, and let your viewers play it. Rotate between 3 different games to keep it fresh. Doesn't matter if you have 1 viewer or 100.000. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/1d299140e4aac56c003362a096797ae4.poster.avif?t=1750364928\" width=624 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/1d299140e4aac56c003362a096797ae4.webm?t=1750364928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/1d299140e4aac56c003362a096797ae4.mp4?t=1750364928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> Cuby is a cute bouncing cube that will swipe away emotes placed by viewers. Emotes that survive Cuby's bouncing rage will gain points! You can also use your profile picture or let it switch between your emotes.<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/710da5eb865926026b90d44dc212dd6d.poster.avif?t=1750364928\" width=624 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/710da5eb865926026b90d44dc212dd6d.webm?t=1750364928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/710da5eb865926026b90d44dc212dd6d.mp4?t=1750364928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> While you are working on the toilet, your viewers are coordinating the defense against alien domination! Look at them go, working together to prioritise targets and reach a new high score.<br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/b62eedd9679ff813499e8620c04017be.poster.avif?t=1750364928\" width=624 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/b62eedd9679ff813499e8620c04017be.webm?t=1750364928\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2956400/extras/b62eedd9679ff813499e8620c04017be.mp4?t=1750364928\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> Dance until you are hit! Who will dance to victory? Perfect for hosting a giveaway. Alternatively, announce 3 options, type !start to play Victory Dance, go take a break, and let the winning viewer decide your next game. <br><br>Take a break while not stressing about decreasing numbers #selfcare💜routine. <br>✅Keeps viewers engaged<br>✅Mods can start new games.<br>✅Replace your countdown timer before the stream starts. Play a game instead.<br><br><strong>DISCLAIMER: Break Games is designed for creators on Twitch, no matter the audience size.</strong>",
